apps.title: Roame - Award Travel
apps.description:
Stop wasting your points. With Roame, you can redeem first and business class for the price of economy.

Roame helps you find flight deals with up to 25 cents per point in redemption value. Instead of searching on the credit card travel portal or multiple airline websites, you can search for award flights across multiple airline loyalty programs simultaneously and in just seconds.

REAL-TIME FLlGHT SEARCH
Search for real-time award flights across more than 28 airline loyalty programs.

FULL AVAILABILITY
We are the only award search tool that allows you to search award availability up to 365 days, any route (domestic & international), any fare class, and airline frequent flyer program.

CREATE ALERTS
Create custom alerts to discover when the best flight deals become available. Airlines release their cheapest saver flights at all hours of the day. Roame will automatically alert you when we find them.

ALL AIRLINE ALLIANCES SUPPORTED
We support all Star Alliance, OneWorld, and SkyTeam award flight routes.

Roame supports the most popular loyalty programs:
+ Air Canada Aeroplan
+ Air France / KLM Flying Blue
+ Alaska Airlines Mileage Plan
+ American Airlines AAdvantage
+ Avianca Lifemiles
+ British Airways Executive Club Avios
+ Cathay Pacific Asia Miles
+ Delta Skymies
+ Emirates Skywards
+ Etihad Guest
+ Iberia Plus
+ jetBlue TrueBlue
+ Lufthansa Miles & More
+ Qantas Frequent Flyer
+ Qatar Airways Privilege Club
+ Singapore Airlines Krisflyer
+ Turkish Airlines Miles&Smiles
+ United MileagePlus
+ Virgin Atlantic Flying Club
+ 8 more loyalty programs


CREDIT CARD POINTS
You can filter flight results by all major credit card transfer programs.
- American Express Membership Rewards
- Chase Ultimate Rewards
- Citi ThankYou Rewards
- Capital One
- BILT Rewards
- Brex
- Ramp
- Wells Fargo Rewards

raw_data.releaseNotes:
What’s New

Captain’s update: we’ve made some exciting improvements and a few key fixes to keep your travel experience running smoothly.

• Fixed deep links so they now open the app correctly when you tap shared flight links.
• Improved the home screen flight loading by program — everything now appears almost instantly to help you explore faster.
• Fixed a strange issue where bonus information on flight cards was being cut off.
• Updated the flight origin and destination search field so results now match perfectly with what you see on the web.
• Added a new post-purchase checklist to help you get the most out of your subscription.
• Programs now display correctly and no longer show results that aren’t actually available.
• Launched eSIMs for all users. You can now purchase and manage them right from your profile.
• Refreshed our app icon with a sleek, glassy new look inspired by the latest iOS design.

As always, we’ve cleaned up a few smaller bugs along the way to make sure your journey with Roame remains smooth from takeoff to landing.
If anything feels off during your trip, our crew is ready at support@roame.travel.

Thanks for flying with Roame.

apps.title: Travel Ladies
apps.description:
Travel Ladies is an app for women who want to meet new people and make friends while traveling. If you’re exploring solo or looking for company, this app helps connect women from all over the world.

Meet new people

Find other women to meet up with while traveling. From new cities to upcoming trips, Travel Ladies makes it easy to discover like-minded women nearby.

Stay with locals

 Stay with local women for free and experience a destination from a personal, authentic perspective. Get to know the culture, explore hidden gems, and create meaningful connections.

Find travel buddies

 Looking for someone to travel with? Find travel buddies who share your destination, dates, and interests. It’s the perfect way to share the adventure and make lasting memories.

Share travel stories

Post photos, share tips, and swap stories with other women around the world. Get inspired by others' journeys and build a community of travel-loving women.


Travel Ladies Plus plans:

Weekly: $4.99
Monthly: $9.99
Annual: $39.99

Payments and Renewal:

Payment will be charged to iTunes Account at confirmation of purchase. Subscription automatically renews unless auto-renew is turned off at least 24-hours before the end of the current period.
Account will be charged for renewal within 24-hours prior to the end of the current period.
You can manage or turn off auto-renew in your Account settings at any time after purchase
No cancellation of the current subscription is allowed during the active period and we are not liable for the cost of your subscription if your account is banned due to violating our terms and service.

Terms of use: https://travelladies.app/terms-and-conditions
Privacy policy: https://travelladies.app/privacy-policy

apps.description:
EUROPAMUNDO VACATIONS
At Europamundo Vacations, we take you on captivating guided tours around the world. We offer flexible tours, full of guarantees, and at the most competitive price. With our app, you can explore our comprehensive travel catalog, get quotes, and manage reservations with our partner agents. This application will become your indispensable travel companion, offering you:

• ON-TOUR: Your Travel Assistant
Get ready to enjoy each day to the fullest with the information and tips your travel assistant will offer as we accompany you on your tour.

• MY-TOURS: All Your Trips in One Place
Here you can store the reservations of your trips with us, your favorite tours, and the quotes of the trips you are planning. You will have access to all the details of your next adventure, including the itinerary, airport transfers, the hotels where you will stay, optional excursions you can add, and more.

• EXPLORE: Your Next Destination Awaits
Browse our complete travel catalog and find your next destination. With our intuitive and effective travel search engine, you can find tours that visit the countries or cities you've always wanted to know. Filter the results according to your needs: starting places, departure dates, customizable trips.

Each trip comes with all the details you need, including itinerary, included services, optional excursions, and more. Plus, we offer you a full gallery of photos and videos so you can get a preview of everything you'll discover with us.

raw_data.releaseNotes: We continue to improve our app to offer you the best experience on your trip.

apps.title: EF Adventures
apps.description:
Say hello to the essential app for travelers. The EF Adventures app supports and connects our global community.

Here’s how we make world travel easy:
• Build your profile so your group can get to know you
• See who’s going on your tour
• Swap tips, ask questions, and chat with your group
• Customize your trip with excursions (even while you’re on tour)
• Make payments quickly and easily
• Complete your checklist to ensure you’re fully prepped for tour
• Receive helpful notifications and status updates as you get ready
• Review entry requirements for countries on your tour
• Sign pre-tour travel forms
• View your flight, hotel, and itinerary details—even without WiFi
• Stay connected to your group and Tour Director throughout the tour
• Use the global currency converter while on-the-go
• Get easy on-tour support access
• Share photos—and lifelong memories—with your group 
• Complete your tour evaluation

We’re always dreaming up ways to give our amazing travel community an even better experience. Keep an eye out for updates as new features are released.

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References

apps.title: FindPenguins: Travel Tracker
apps.description:
Millions of travelers trust FindPenguins, the first travel app of its kind. Plan, track, and share your trip — all in one. Instantly transform your journey into flyover videos vividly visualizing your travel route. Build your own unique travel profile by adding your places, photos, and stories — capturing memories that last a lifetime. And with just a wink, turn these memories into a carefully-designed hardcover travel book.

Activate our Travel Tracker to automatically record your travel route — battery-friendly and offline, with your phone in your pocket. Write posts about the places you visit, and let FindPenguins take care of the rest.

PLAN YOUR TRIP
Assemble your itinerary, upload essential travel documents, and have everything at your fingertips. Explore itineraries from fellow travelers to inspire your bucket list and effortlessly plan your next adventure. With access to an archive of over 10 million travel experiences, you can see places as they truly are.

TRACK WITH EASE
Automatically track and log your path on an interactive world map. Have complete control over your privacy, with the option to share your live location with a time delay. Add photos, videos, and travel stories, whether solo or alongside fellow travelers. Create an archive of your travel memories that lets you relive your journeys anytime, anywhere.

SHARING BRINGS JOY
Generate exciting 3D flyover videos of your recorded route — free and in seconds. Share your trip with family and friends in a fun, inviting way. Follow other travelers, stay connected with your loved ones, or find inspiration for future adventures.

WHAT ELSE?

“FindPenguins is the perfect network for travelers.”
— Lonely Planet Traveller

“We are committed to creating the most beautiful travel diary app on the market. Design, usability, and honesty are at the heart of everything we do.”
— Tobias, CEO

“In 2013, FindPenguins pioneered modern travel tracking apps and has prioritized development over marketing ever since.”
— Inside-Fact

TELL US HOW WE’RE DOING
Leave us a review if you’re enjoying your FindPenguins app experience or head over to our help page for further assistance: support.findpenguins.com

advisories: Infrequent/Mild Alcohol, Tobacco, or Drug Use or References

Loved & Trusted by Over 20 Million Users!
Rated 4.6+ stars on the App Store
Trusted by millions for smarter spending, saving, and earning

Secure & trusted – Used by millions of Americans to save, earn, and build credit

apps.title: GeoEx
apps.description:
The GeoEx app allows GeoEx travelers to access their itineraries and travel documents on any mobile device. You may download this app for free, however in order to see an itinerary or any other trip preparation documents you must be booked on a GeoEx trip.
 
Notable features of the GeoEx app:
- Changes and updates to your itinerary are displayed in real time. You’ll always see the most up to date version of your itinerary.
- Offline access of the itinerary and any attached documents – you can access your itinerary and trip documents even when you’re not in wifi. Whether you’re on a plane, in the airport terminal, or in a car on the way to the hotel you’ll be able to access any information you need.
- Consolidates all details into one interface that you can take with you wherever you go.
- Old travel itineraries remain on the app to provide inspiration for the future and to share details about your trip no matter where you go.
 
GeoEx is an adventure travel company that provides high-end custom and small-group travel to the world’s most astonishing places. www.geoex.com 
 
Send any feedback or feature requests to itineraries@geoex.com.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
- Update the app icon
- Bug fixing and performance improvement.

tTravel is a mobile app developed by travelers for travelers.

Discover the best travel spots, plan your adventures with ease, and enjoy a unique and meaningful travel experience – all while saving money!

With tTravel, you can start gathering inspiration well before your trip, have a ready-made plan for any situation, receive unique and valuable advice while on location, and explore itineraries from around the world. Whether you're capturing your journey, planning the perfect getaway, or looking for affordable travel options, tTravel is your ultimate travel partner.

Perfect for solo explorers, travel enthusiasts, and anyone looking to make the most of their journeys!

apps.title: GBTA
apps.description: The Global Business Travel Association (GBTA) is the world’s premier business travel and meetings trade organization headquartered in the Washington, D.C. area with operations on six continents. GBTA’s members manage more than $345 billion of global business travel and meetings expenditures annually. GBTA delivers world-class education, events, research, advocacy, and media to a growing global network of more than 28,000 travel professionals and 125,000 active contacts. Our focus is to equip our members with the knowledge and resources necessary to navigate the rapidly changing business travel landscape resulting in improved managed travel programs, top line business growth, and exemplary careers.

apps.title: Breeze Travel Inc
apps.description:
BREEZE brings travelers and travel companies together for seamless personalized trip discovery and management in one super-app. Our AI-driven platform ensures that travel is smooth, sustainable and pleasurable at every stage of the journey. A growing feature set allows users to do everything from booking great experiences to enjoying eSIM connectivity. Welcome to a refreshing new era where travel is a breeze—effortless, mindful, and joyful.

Breeze super app for frictionless travel replacing 20+ single-purpose apps!

For global travelers, Breeze provides international roaming at a fraction of the cost with eSIM activation in seconds. Stop searching for WiFi and stay connected in over 200 countries - a must have for smooth travel!
Easy duty-free browsing enroute with built in price and availability tracking means you arrive with everything you need.
Streamline all travel logistics from departure to arrival in a single dashboard: from real-time flight updates, hotel & rideshare details, local time zone & weather info, and food recommendations. 
What's more, Breeze automatically crafts your personal travel journal when you capture photos and videos in your timeline. Save, share, and revisit your favorite travel moments!

apps.title: Funliday - Travel Planner
apps.description:
Funliday is a trip planning app that makes your trip easier!!
-- Featured on the 「App store home page」
-- Featured in 「Best New Apps」

Fun + Holiday = Funliday
The best trip planning App in the world!!!

Funliday is a trip planning app that makes your trip easier, helps you and your travel companions to manage your trips, find local attractions, get directions, collaborate with travel companions. Funliday provides thousands of destinations, you can easily explore all of the places you are interested in and simply add them to the itinerary. You can also organize schedules and routes, as well as co-editing with travel companions.

------Key Features-------
* Edit together with others in the same trip. 
* Explore attractions all over the world.
* Organize your trip with ease.
* Offers offline trips (except maps).
* Provides driving/walking/public transit directions.
* Add attractions to Funliday in iOS Safari with share extension.
* Share your trip itinerary by email , WhatsApp and Line.

Like it, love it? Leave us feedback and a rating to let us know! We're all ears for your suggestions on how to improve, so if you've got any (or even if you just want to say hi!), drop us a message at willie@funliday.com. Have fun on your holiday!

Find exclusive discounts on hotels, flights, and travel packages that combine hotel and airfare for your favorite destinations. Enjoy a faster, intuitive interface designed to provide you with the best booking experience.

Main features:
• Book now, pay later: Plan without worrying about immediate payment.
• Interest-free months: Make your payments easier with flexible financing options.
• Free cancellation: Cancel at no cost at thousands of hotels worldwide.
• New look and intuitive design: Navigate quickly and easily to find your next destination.
• Customized filters: Find flights and hotels that fit your budget and needs with filters for price, category, location, and more.
• Detailed galleries and descriptions: Explore images and complete details of hotels and their rooms.
• Secure booking: Pay quickly and securely from the app with total confidence.
• Your itinerary always handy: Keep your itinerary and travel details at your fingertips.
• Travel packages (Hotel + Flight): Save by booking complete packages that include both flight and hotel for maximum enjoyment.

Download PriceTravel now and access exclusive offers on flights, hotels, and travel packages. Plan your vacations, weekend getaways, or business trips easily and enjoy the best rates at all your destinations.

apps.title: Engine Corporate Travel
apps.description:
Engine gives you the flexibility to change travel plans, visibility into trends, and total control to prevent overspending. Smarter, faster, more powerful tools for business travel all on one platform. Welcome to modern travel management.

 

More Savings

Save time and money with powerful business tools like custom travel policies, real-time expenditure tracking, and consolidated billing. You can also save an average of 26% on hotels with our exclusive discounts. 

More Choice

From your favorite airlines and hotels (with over 750,000 properties) to your preferred car rental agencies, we’ve got you covered. Discover what makes us the fastest growing business travel platform in the country. 

More Rewards

Your loyalty points just got a bonus. Earn Engine Rewards on all lodging and rental car reservations in addition to your favorite travel loyalty programs.

More Flexibility

When plans change we’re here for you. Get refunds for last-minute cancellations and shortened trips by booking with Flex, and instantly extend a trip with just a few clicks.

apps.title: Expensify - Travel & Expense
apps.description:
Expensify helps more than 15 million people around the world track expenses, reimburse employees, manage corporate cards, send invoices, pay bills, and book travel. All at the speed of chat.

Expensify is built for:

* Self-employed: Track and categorize expenses for budgeting or tax purposes. Scan receipts, log distance, or just type in an amount. Send invoices to clients and chat with them in the same place.
* Small business owners: Say goodbye to spreadsheets. Keep employees happy with easy expense management and quick reimbursements. Clear up any questions in a chat on the expense or report level. Sync with QuickBooks Online, Xero, and more.
* Growing teams: Scale up your spend management with the Expensify corporate card, built-in travel booking and trip chat rooms, and multi-level approval workflows. Sync with Sage Intacct, NetSuite, and more.
* Enterprise companies: Reimburse employees in every country. Manage expenses in every currency. Import transactions from every type of corporate or personal card.

Key features:

* Chat: Keep your money moving with realtime chat built into every type of transaction.
* Receipt scanning: Snap a picture of any receipt and SmartScan extracts the details.
* Distance tracking: Log miles or kilometers on a beautiful map, at custom rates.
* Manual expenses: No receipt? Just type in an amount. Still better than a spreadsheet.
* Categorization: Code your expenses once and then we’ll learn to do it for you.
* Submissions: Expenses auto-submit in realtime, or you can set a custom cadence.
* Approvals: Add one or more expense approvers to your workflow for more control.
* Expense chat: Questions about an expense? Ask and approve in the same place.
* Reimbursements: Pay back your employees at home or around the world.
* Expensify Card: Get up to 2% cash back on all US purchases and save on your bill.
* Corporate cards: Give your team the Expensify Card or import your own.
* Invoices: Send, view, discuss, and pay invoices in a chat. No more app + email combos.
* Travel: Book flights, hotels, and rental cars right in the app. T&E at its finest.
* Trip rooms: A chat room for every trip to organize expenses and answer questions.
* Accounting: Sync with QuickBooks, Xero, Sage Intacct, NetSuite, and more.
* Security: 2FA, PCI-DSS Level 1, SOC1 and SOC2 Type II Certified.
* Other integrations: Uber, Lyft, Delta, ADP, Gusto, Zenefits, Workday, and more.

Run your back office at the speed of chat. Download Expensify today.

The Expensify Visa® Commercial Card is issued by The Bancorp Bank, N.A., Member FDIC, pursuant to a license from Visa U.S.A. Inc. and may not be used at all merchants that accept Visa cards.

apps.title: Pocket Travel
apps.description:
Pocket Travel  is a revolutionary travel itinerary management tool that lets travel professionals collaborate, consolidate, and innovate travel plans with their clients. Travelers may use this app for free, however they must sign up with a Signature Travel Network travel agency that uses this system to enjoy the app.

Notable Pocket Travel features:

- Travel details are displayed on a shared screen as plans come together, empowering travelers and their travel advisors to collaborate in real-time. 
- Consolidates every detail into one dynamic, paperless interface that travelers can take with them wherever they go. From air to theater tickets, hotel to dining reservations, the entire itinerary is at your fingertips.
- Archives travel itineraries to provide inspiration for the future.
- Integrates Maps so travelers always know how to get to their next stop. 
- Allows for offline access, so travelers always have the important travel information they need.

Travel is exciting, and planning it should be too. Make conversations more productive, and eliminate last-minute stress with the Pocket Travel  App.

Support: support@pockettravelconsultant.com

apps.title: World Travel Stories - Airport
apps.description:
Attention all passengers, please fasten your seatbelts and prepare to land in an all-new adventure with World Travel Stories™. Stow your belongings and get ready to EXPLORE! Tour the all-new exciting locations, chock full of crazy interactions with your favorite characters!

World Travel Stories™ will drop you off in a packed airport, and what happens next is completely up to you. You are in charge of creating your own traveling stories. There are no rules. No limits. Drag and drop your characters anywhere, dress them in any way, and interact with loads of exciting objects in lively new environments across the globe.

The world is yours! Use your imagination to create the most amazing stories yet. Hit up the airport and travel to exotic new locations, all around the world. Imagine being a jetsetter, or maybe a jungle explorer in mystic ruins? What wondrous things will you discover in these remote destinations? With new locations waiting for you on frequent updates, the possibilities are limitless.

Uncover the mysteries of an ancient temple, marvel in the majestic waterfalls, or just chill out in the pool of a tropical eco-resort with a juicy tropical cocktail. Find out for yourself in this extraordinary adventure today!


**Features**

- Free play mode you’ll love. Your world, your rules.
- Exotic new locations full of charming customizable characters.
- Lightning-fast traveling from one location to another.
- Game progress is auto-saved. Continue your amazing story the next day.
- Capture the most magical moments during your adventures with the Camera mode.
- New updates will just roll in, with additional destinations, characters, and an insane amount of things to do.

The first free destination includes a vibrant city, a cozy travelers’ home, and a cutting-edge international airport, with thousands of interactions and 19 cool characters. A great beginning to start your journey.


**SUBARA for everyone**

We build digital experiences that are filled with fun and creativity, that spark the imagination of millions of players, of any age, from any corner of the world.

Our ethos is underpinned by the quest of being the best humans, and company, we can be. Whether this is through planting trees to help rebuild the world, or by producing great games to entertain, educate, and enlighten players while inspiring them to be the best version of themselves.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Travel just got an upgrade!

• Improved performance for faster, smoother play
• Smoother transitions between locations
• Fixed a few pesky bugs hiding in your suitcase
• More surprises waiting at every destination

Update now and keep the adventures going!

apps.title: Mindtrip: AI Travel Companion
apps.description:
Whether you’re navigating a buzzing city or escaping to somewhere serene, Mindtrip is always in your pocket — ready to help you do it better (and yes, it’s totally free).

See and manage your entire itinerary, including any bookings you’ve forwarded. Get smart suggestions on where to eat, stay and go based on your vibe and location. Map your route, check what’s nearby and easily add new stops.

Ask anything along the way and get instant AI-powered answers — plus trusted tips from real travelers and local experts. Need to shift gears? Update your plans on the fly. Traveling with others? Invite them to join your trip and make memories together, stress free.

Mindtrip puts everything you need for smart, seamless travel at your fingertips — personalized, organized and always a step ahead. You explore. We’ll handle the rest.


What’s in the App

• Organized Info: Access your itinerary and bookings all in one place — so you always know what’s next. Just forward any confirmations or receipts to receipts@mindtrip.ai, and we’ll take care of the rest.

• Personalized Recs: Tell us how you like to travel and we’ll tailor our suggestions for where to stay, eat and explore to fit your vibe.

• Explore Nearby: See what’s worthwhile based on where you are — or where you’re planning to go. Zoom the map, check distances and add picks right to your trip plan.

• AI Insights: Ask anything, anytime and get instant, AI-powered answers. 

• Human Expertise: Browse guides created by local experts — and see their tips featured on place pages as real-world proof of what’s actually good. 

• Magic Camera: Not sure what you’re looking at? Take a pic and we’ll tell you what it is — and why it matters.

• Language Translation: Snap a photo of a sign, menu or label, and get an instant translation — no need for guessing.

• Real-Time Planning: Add or update your custom trip plans on the fly.

• Collaboration Tools: Traveling with others? Invite them to join your trip and explore together.

Mindtrip isn’t just for planning. It changes how you see the world — with everything you need, right when you need it.


We Love Feedback
We’re on a mission to make Mindtrip your ultimate travel companion — and your feedback helps shape what comes next. Got a feature idea, something you’re loving or something that could be better? Drop us a line at hello@mindtrip.ai and help make the app (and your next adventure) even better.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
• Start Anywhere: Scrolling the web or socials and spot travel inspo? Tap the share icon, choose Mindtrip and instantly turn it into a chat, collection or trip plan.

• Google Pins: Already saving places in Google Maps? Tap the share icon, choose Mindtrip and instantly turn your pins into a collection you can plan from.

• Bug Fixes: We ironed out some kinks to make your experience smoother and more reliable.

apps.title: YouTravel.me
apps.description:
YouTravel.me - small group adventures with Travel Experts around the world. Save money and time by traveling with like-minded travelers through YouTravel.me.
 
Adventures in small groups with like-minded people, perfectly suited to your interests
- Multi-day tours in small groups
- 6,000+ real reviews
- Easy online booking from pre-vetted tour organizers

A small group adventure is a new way to travel that doesn't require a tour operator. Accompanied by an independent travel expert who knows the country exceptionally well, you’ll deep dive into the local culture and customs.
You have the opportunity to embark on a travel-expert's tour in a small group of like-minded people, which means you experience an adventure of a lifetime. Meals, lodging, and activities are all included. All you need to do is arrive at the starting point.

Our Mission:
Our platform enables every individual to break through the limits of their world and take their journey to a whole new level.
 
 
You no longer have to search the Internet and plan your own trip. We have done that for you! Thousands of unique adventures await you in 120+ countries!
The search won’t take long — we’ve already hand-picked the best tours. You can sort and filter results to find the perfect one for you quickly.
While travel memories are priceless, it's always a good idea to ensure you get a good deal. We've negotiated the best price with the organizers, so you won't find a cheaper adventure anywhere else.
In addition, you can directly contact the organizer. No managers and no waiting. Make your trip even more unique by asking any questions you have to the tour leader.

With all-in-one pricing, no hidden fees, and no extra charges, you can plan and book seamlessly knowing you’re paying the best price with no surprise fees. Discover Canada's fastest growing online travel company when you download the FlightHub app today!

apps.title: The Points Guy: Travel Rewards
apps.description:
Create an account to unlock the world of points & miles with The Points Guy App. Maximize your spending, earn rewards faster, and easily track all of your points and all of your miles all in one place.

With over 70 loyalty programs supported and growing, The Points Guy App is your one-stop-shop for tracking exactly how to maximize your spending, points earning, and points redemptions across every card and program specific to you.

Connecting the dots from earning points on every purchase to turning those points into travel realities can seem complicated and full of hoops to jump through, especially if you're new to the world of credit cards, points and miles. The Points Guy App is here to help you navigate that journey at every step -- using the best credit card for your spending habits, earning valuable points on every purchase, learning about loyalty programs and transfer partners, and redeeming your points at the best value for you, whether that's visiting family for the weekend or planning the trip of a lifetime.

Optimize your spending habits and learn how to make your next trip a reality with:

THE TPG DASHBOARD
Tailor your TPG experience with the completely customizable dashboard. Check in daily to track your rewards and welcome offers, compare monthly earned points to missed points, and get a snapshot of your recent transaction history. Don't forget you can also use tools like our "Card Advisor" to get recommendations of nearby places to use your best card and continue to maximize your rewards.

YOUR WALLET
See your points net worth across all cards and programs by syncing your accounts. Learn how to maximize every purchase with in-depth breakdowns of your cards and spending categories. Add your airline and hotel loyalty programs to see your points and statuses, and use the transfer partner calculator to see how to get the most out of your points. 

Plus, updated benefit tracking for cards helps you get the most value out of all the benefits you receive with your cards and lets you know when they are about to expire.

A CURATED NEWS FEED
Stay up to date with travel news: Get up to speed with the latest TPG content anytime, anywhere with a customizable feed of the articles you care about. From credit card reviews to personal trip experiences to breaking news, our experts have the inside scoop on all things travel.

Across the 70+ institutions supported, you can choose to connect your account for automated tracking or add cards, points or miles without connecting to manage your rewards manually. Some of the secure bank connections you can make include:
- American Express (AmEx)
- Bank of America (BoFa)
- Barclays
- Capital One
- Chase
- Citi
- Discover
- Wells Fargo

The TPG App also supports --
Airline loyalty programs like:
- Air Canada Aeroplan
- Air France Flying Blue
- Alaska Mileage Plan

- Southwest Rapid Rewards
- United MileagePlus
- Virgin Atlantic Flying Club
Hotel loyalty programs like:
- Best Western Rewards
- Choice Privileges
- Hilton Honors
- IHG Rewards Club
- Marriott Bonvoy
- Radisson Rewards
- World of Hyatt
- Wyndham Rewards
And additional valuable loyalty programs you may want to connect like:
- Amazon Rewards
- Amtrak Guest Rewards
- Diners Club Rewards
- Disney Rewards
- Expedia Rewards
- Lowe's
- Walmart Rewards

apps.title: Air NZ
apps.description:
The Air NZ app – your trusted travel companion – lets you:

• Take control of your flight bookings – change your seat, add a bag, manage your meals, and more.

• Check in online, from anywhere, and access your digital boarding pass in the app, or add it to Apple Wallet.

• Scan your digital boarding pass to print bag tags at the kiosk, board your aircraft, and if you're eligible, enter the Air New Zealand lounge.

• Hold up to 9 boarding passes for your group or family under the same booking. Bookings with infants can't currently be supported.

• Have real-time flight info at your fingertips with up-to-date gate and seat info, boarding and departure times, and more.

• Receive notifications with key flight information – you'll never miss a beat.

• Order coffee from your phone, and we'll let you know when it's ready to collect. Air New Zealand lounge access required.

• Purchase travel-related services such as travel insurance, parking, airport taxis and shuttles, hotels, and rental cars.

• Track your Airpoints Dollars™ and Status Points balances, view your benefits and latest activity, or access your digital Airpoints™ card straight from your phone, plus find Airpoints Partners to help you earn Airpoints Dollars every day.

• Access and use your digital Koru card when you have a Koru membership.

• Access quick links to book or change flights on the fly.

• Stay organised – add flight details to your calendar, and share them with others.

Things not as effortless as they could be? We'd love to hear from you. Use the 'Help and Feedback' menu in the Air NZ app to see your options.

By downloading, installing and using the Air NZ app, you agree that you have read, understood and agree to our Website and App Terms of Use at airnewzealand.co.nz/website-terms-of-use and our Privacy Policy at airnewzealand.co.nz/privacy.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Kia ora!
We’ve made improvements and fixed bugs to ensure a smoother experience.

Thanks for flying with Air New Zealand!

apps.title: TripSoda : Travel Community
apps.description:
A travel community for the world's travellers,

There's nowhere we can't go and nothing we can't do!


1. Travelling companion communities

- Find different types of travelling companions in our country-specific travelling companion communities.Feel free to chat with your travelling companions. Travelling together is more fun!
- From Europe, Asia, North America, South America, and Africa to domestic travelling companions, you'll find travelling companions in every continent, country, and city!
- Full, partial, meal, tour, accommodation sharing, co-purchase, and more! There are many different types of travelling companions!
- You can also chat, meet, and travel with live travel companions, travel buddies, foreign friends, and local friends near you right now!

2. Travel information sharing community

- Share various travel information in country-specific communities! You can communicate with more travellers with the light and fast post function!
- Food, places and spots to visit, travel tips, real-time travel information, and various travel events! Join the TripSoda travel community!
- You'll find helpful travel tips from travel influencers, travel YouTubers, travel Instagrammers, and travel agents!

3. TripSoda's exclusive travel shop

- Buy and participate in adventure, exploration, challenge, and experience trips that are unique to TripSoda!
- From Mongolia, Central Asia, South America, Africa, and more, you'll find adventure and exploration travel experiences!
- Tours, activities, leisure, snaps, car hire, travel insurance, accommodation in Japan, and more at the lowest prices around the world!

4. Prepare, travel, and record your trips all on TripSoda!

- Customise your traveller profile and document your travels. Personalise your travel business card with a variety of content.
- Customise your travel profile with your travel tastes and personalise it with photos and content to create your own travel business card.
- Get reviews from your travelling companions and friends to build a trusted profile. Keep a travelogue of your travels.
- Connect with trusted travellers with a variety of verifications. Check out Kakao, Instagram, and mobile phone verification.
- Track your trips with Tripcards and Triplog to see what other travellers have been up to.
- Filter and search to connect with travellers who match your age, gender, travel preferences, itinerary, and travel plans.

If you haven't found satisfaction with existing travel apps, Tripsoda offers a fresh perspective. 
Explore a new way to connect, plan, and experience travel beyond your expectations!

apps.description:
ONEApp fits all your travel needs:
 
Pre-order Duty Free Online
Pre-order Food & Beverages at Adani-managed Airports
Flight Tracker – Baggage Belt & Gate Number Info
Unlimited Free Airport Wi-Fi
Book Airport Car Parking
Book Pranaam Meet & Greet Service
Book Porter Service
Book Airport Cabs
Apply/Manage Adani One ICICI Bank Credit Cards
Scan Here to Complete Payments for Shopping at Adani-managed Airport
Airport Lounge
Special Assistance
Adani Reward Program
Forex
Airport Maps & Navigation
Book Flights, Hotels, Trains & Buses
Pay Bills
 
…and much more. Download the app and take it for a spin.
 
*Enjoy great deals and discounts on Adani OneApp*
   
*Get assured Adani OneApp Rewards on every eligible transaction*
 
*Redeem 100% of the points on your next transaction*
 
Explore Duty Free on Adani OneApp and shop from a diverse selection of products from global brands, including premium chocolates, cosmetics, fashion accessories, bags, toys, electronics and much more. Simply pre-order your favourite products online and collect them at the airport.
 
Food and Beverages at the airport can now be pre-ordered on the go, allowing you to explore the menu even before entering the airport and skip the queue at the counter. Make every meal DEALicious with great offers on every order.
 
Stay updated with our flight tracker! Get real-time flight status, flight live status, airport status, airport arrivals, departures, gate info, baggage details & more. Easily check flight status and airline status on the go.
 
Unlock unlimited free Wi-Fi at the airport with Adani OneApp. Connect to superfast Wi-Fi available throughout the terminals and stay in touch with your loved ones or plan your work and travel on the go.
 
Airport car parking is now seamless and efficient. Effortlessly find airport parking spots, check real-time parking availability, and book right from your phone. Whether you're looking for long-term airport parking, short-term parking, or premium airport parking services, Adani OneApp makes it easy to plan and park with confidence.
 
Pranaam Meet & Greet Service adds exclusivity to your airport experience. Select the type of Pranaam Service package that suits your needs, and get airport assistance from a dedicated Pranaam executive to escort you for a hassle-free experience.
 
Porter service ensures a smooth and hands-free travel experience. From the drop-off point at departures to the airline check-in counters, our porter team will make your journey comfortable.
 
Airport Cabs are now guaranteed to be waiting for you, with zero surcharges and zero cancellations by the driver.
 
Adani One ICICI Bank Credit Cards powered by Visa offer a host of benefits, discounts, and rewards. Signature or Platinum, both cards are your gateway to unparalleled benefits and features in collaboration with ICICI Bank.
 
Payments at Adani-managed airports are quick and easy, thanks to our Scan Here feature on Adani OneApp. You can also earn Adani OneApp Rewards on every eligible transaction.
 
Relax, work, or enjoy complimentary food and drinks in our airport lounges—featuring Wi-Fi, business facilities, and premium comfort. Now, book your lounge access online for a seamless start to your journey.
 
Earn Adani OneApp Rewards on every eligible transaction done on Adani OneApp and redeem them to book services across the app. 1 AdaniOne App Reward = ₹1. You can redeem 100% of your collected Rewards on any or every transaction.
 
Enjoy the facility of currency exchange for outbound and inbound travellers. You may utilize an array of Forex services on offer.
 
Adani OneApp is your all-in-one travel companion—book cheap flights, find top hotels at the best prices, reserve train tickets via India’s trusted IRCTC platform, and easily book bus tickets with just a few taps.
 
Pay bills anytime, anywhere with Adani OneApp—electricity, gas, mobile, landline, LPG, and FASTag—seamlessly powered by BBPS.
 
See you on board!

Join Us Today

apps.title: Lambus | Travel Planner
apps.description:
Lambus - Your all-in-one travel companion!

Conquer the world with ease and plan your next adventure with Lambus - the ultimate travel app that has everything you need for your trip! From trip planning to organizing your documents to managing expenses, we've got it all under control so you can focus on your adventure! Whether you're traveling solo or on a group adventure, Lambus is your reliable companion on every trip.

# Simply plan, experience more!
So much world, so little time! That's why we've made itinerary planning as easy as possible. Mark your destinations as stops and add interesting places effortlessly. Want to change something? No problem! Move or delete your stops in a snap. Planning your trip has never been so easy!

# Import itineraries made easy
Whether you're planning a bike tour, motorcycle tour or hiking adventure - with Lambus you can easily import .gpx files from popular manufacturers like Garmin and all participants of your trip will have instant access to the itineraries. Or you can simply create a new route directly in our route planner.

# Everything in one place - No more chaos in your documents
No more confusing lists and lost emails! With Lambus, you collect all your travel documents in one safe place. So you (and your travel companions) can access them at any time, even offline!

# Keep travel expenses under control
Lambus makes it easy to keep track of your travel expenses. You're on a group trip and want to split the expenses? No problem! We'll even do the math for you! Just fill in the form, calculate your debts and pay directly.

# Manage practical notes
Whether you want to share your Airbnb PIN code with the group, create a packing list, or just jot down your passport number, Lambus helps you manage notes easily and securely.

# Get inspired!
Still no idea where to go next? Browse through our Discover feature and get inspired by the many destinations. Whether it's an exciting road trip through the USA, a city break in a European metropolis or a relaxing beach vacation - you'll find it here. Every day we publish exciting trips with stops and travel tips!

# Book your tickets
With our transportation feature, you can not only plan routes between stops, but also easily deposit or book your transportation. Once you book your tickets, they are automatically added to your travel documents!

Visiting more than one place? Lambus is the ultimate travel app for backpackers, road trippers and world travelers! Plan your next adventure effortlessly with our innovative travel planner. What are you waiting for? Download Lambus and start your next adventure with us!

Aviata.kz — авиабилеты на рейсы более 1000 авиакомпаний в одном приложении: FlyArystan, Air Astana, Scat, Qazaq Air, Аэрофлот, Победа, Belavia, Lufthansa, KLM, Turkish Airlines и многие другие. 

Сравнение цен 
Показываем варианты цен от других онлайн агентств и от самих авиакомпаний. Теперь вам не нужно заходить на сайты авиакомпаний или агентств, чтобы сравнить цены с нашими –– это можно сделать сразу на Авиате. Если вам понравилось предложение от другого агентства или авиакомпании, можно просто кликнуть на цену и перейти на их сайт для покупки.

Удобные фильтры
Фильтруйте результаты поиска по цене, авиакомпаниям и времени вылета. Например, вы можете указать, чтобы поиск выдавал только прямые рейсы, возвратные или только с багажом.

Сохранение пассажиров
Сохраните информацию о пассажирах в приложении. Больше не нужно каждый раз заполнять вручную информацию о пассажирах. Запишите или отсканируйте паспортные данные один раз и пользуйтесь постоянно.

apps.title: Let's Travel Magazine
apps.description:
Let’s Travel – the magazine that starts your journey.

Planning a trip through New Zealand, Australia, the Pacific Islands or global destinations throughout USA, Europe, The Middle East & Asia? Then Let’s Travel is for YOU!

Hand-picked, award winning writers and photographers will whet your appetite for a taste of travel like never before!

Found in the very best hotels and airline lounges and now available digitally to YOU!

Copious quantities of travel, adventure and pure hedonism as we traverse the globe in search of new and exciting journeys for you to undertake the next time you're planning a get-away. We also cover festivals, carnivals, and other events.

We'll take you along on our magical ride as we travel by:
Land – ride the rails, pitch a tent, take the RV off the beaten track, or hitch a ride on a camel;
Sea – cruise the world's liners, charter private vessels, find that perfect catch;
Air - from airline reviews to hot air balloons, if it's aloft, we'll try it!

Luxury, family, adventure, adrenalin ... there's something for every taste and budget!

Come along for the ride ... we know you'll have the time of your life!

----------------------
Further future issues and back issues can be purchased within the app. 
Subscriptions are also available within the application.

Available subscriptions are: 

6 months: £7.99/ AUS$ 12.99 (3 Issues) 
12 months: £13.99/ AUS$ 20.99 (6 Issues) 

-The subscription will renew automatically unless cancelled more than 24 hours before the end of the current period, you will be charged for renewal within 24 hours of the end of the current period, for the same duration and at the current subscription rate for the product. 
-You may turn off the auto-renewal of subscriptions through your Account Settings, however you are not able to cancel the current subscription during its active period. 
-Payment will charged to your iTunes account at confirmation of purchase and any unused portion of a free trial period, if offered, will be forfeited when a subscription to that publication is purchased 

Bundles of single issues can be also be bought within the application. To use purchased credits, simply click on the issue price and select ‘use credit’. This allows you to purchase back issues at reduced prices. 

Users can register for/ login to a pocketmags account in-app. This will protect their issues in the case of a lost device and allow browsing of purchases on multiple platforms. Existing pocketmags users can retrieve their purchases by logging into their account. 

We recommend loading the app for the first time in a wi-fi area so that all issue data is retrieved. 
If your app will not load past the splash page after a first install or an update please delete and reinstall the app from the App Store 

Help and frequently asked questions be accessed in-app and on pocketmags. 
If you have any problems at all please do not hesitate to contact us: help@pocketmags.com 
-------------------- 
You can find our privacy policy here: 
http://www.pocketmags.com/privacy.aspx 
You can find our terms and conditions here: 
http://www.pocketmags.com/terms.aspx

raw_data.releaseNotes:
This app has been updated by Apple to display the Apple Watch app icon.

Improved reading experience
iPhone X support
Bug fixes and other improvements
**We always love to hear your feedback. If you have any comments or queries please contact us at help@pocketmags.com**

apps.title: Tourist - Travel Planner
apps.description:
Your AI Travel Planner! Choose a destination and select what you want, AI will create your trip in seconds! Edit Places, Take Notes, See everywhere on Map, Ask Questions to ChatBot!

Tourist is the perfect travel companion for all kinds of trips, whether it's a road trip, solo travel, couple getaway, or group adventure. This all-in-one travel app lets you explore professional guides, discover top places, create detailed itineraries, and share your travel experiences effortlessly.

Key Features:

• AI-Powered Trip Planner: Create personalized travel itineraries with ease using our AI feature. Just choose your travel preferences, and trip will be created for you. You can even ask questions about your travel plans through the chatbot, making your planning even simpler.

• Discover City Guides: Explore detailed city guides on an interactive travel map.

• Read and Create Blogs: Read blogs by fellow travelers or create your own to share with the community.

• Easiest Trip Planner: Create your dream trip in minutes and visualize it on a beautiful map.

• One-Click Itineraries: Add activities from top guides directly to your itinerary with just one click.

• Share Experiences: Share your travel experiences and inspire others.

• Collaborate with Friends: Plan trips with friends, split expenses easily, and add real-time updates to your travel plans.

• Notes and Checklists: Add notes to your stops and manage your travel checklist effortlessly.

• Offline Access: Download your travel plans for offline access and stay on track without an internet connection.

• Customize Your Map: Personalize your travel map and change the colors to suit your style.

• Comprehensive Checklists: Keep track of your travel essentials with customizable checklists.

• Discover Events and Festivals: Stay updated on the latest events, festivals, and activities worldwide.

• Traveler Stories: Read inspiring travel stories from other adventurers.

• Plan Road Trips: Add unlimited stops, explore places, and optimize your route for the perfect road trip.

• Explore 40+ Categories: Discover places to visit from over 40 different categories including cafes, restaurants, activities, and more.

Detailed Travel Guides:
Save time searching and focus on your travel dreams with curated travel guides from our editors and fellow travelers. Find top attractions, restaurants, and activities all in one place.

View Plans on a Map:
Add places to your travel plan and see them pinned on an interactive map. Export your itinerary to Google Maps or use Tourist's eye-catching map for a seamless experience.

Collaborate with Friends:
Traveling with friends? Plan together, add places in real-time, and let everyone view or edit the travel plan.

Find the Best Places to Go:
Discover key info like descriptions, photos, user ratings, reviews, opening hours, addresses, and contact details for all places. Stay inspired with top travel guides and add places to your itinerary with one click.

Offline Itinerary Storage:
Download your travel plans for offline access. No internet? No problem! Access your itinerary and find places to visit on the go.

Split Expenses:
Manage trip expenses easily. Add expenses, choose who pays, and avoid the hassle of splitting costs manually.

Explore Anytime:
Even when you're not traveling, catch the latest events, festivals, and activities around the world. Enjoy travel videos and the drive & listen function.

Videos Over Photos:
Experience destinations through video content from popular spots. Add places to your plan or just enjoy the videos for inspiration.

Plan Your Next Adventure with Tourist!
Whether you're planning a quick getaway or a detailed road trip, Tourist has everything you need to make your trip unforgettable. Download now and start exploring!

raw_data.releaseNotes: Tourist just got even better! You should definitely try it! The Activity page is now available in the United States! Each trip plan now includes at least 16 places with AI support! The Travel Assistant works much better and smoother! Trip planners can now easily add photos with this latest feature! Happy planning!

apps.title: Global Entry Mobile
apps.description:
The Global Entry mobile application enables active Global Entry members to report their arrival at any supported airport in the place of a stationary Global Entry portal. You must be an active member in the Global Entry program to use this app.

Simply choose your arrival airport from list of supported airports and submit a photo of yourself to CBP for verification. Be sure to complete this process while you are physically located within your arrival terminal. Once you’ve successfully submitted, you will receive a receipt of your submission that you must present to a Global Entry officer upon arrival. Be prepared to offer further travel documentation upon request. If you are unable to obtain a receipt using the mobile app, you can proceed to an existing Global Entry Portal and proceed with the normal process

The Global Entry mobile application also allows existing Global Entry members to store their CBP Pass ID and (if applicable) select their preferred Class of Admission that will be used by all Global Entry services.

Note: If you are not enrolled in the Global Entry program, you are not eligible to use this mobile application. This app does not enable enrollment for the Global Entry program. You must either proceed with the normal entry process or use the free CBP Mobile Passport Control app.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Changes
- Added support for more liquid glass features

apps.title: Nomadago: Your Travel Network
apps.description:
Nomadago is the hub for your traveling network. We make staying connected with friends easy or finding new ones along the way!
Check out where a friend is going next month, invite the crew to a week in London, or discuss which apartment is best in Lima. Nomadago is a nomad’s social network.

So what makes Nomadago useful?

PERSONAL TRAVEL COMMUNITY

Add your friends and never lose touch with the people that you meet traveling. Create your network of traveling friends and easily plan when you’ll see each other next.

TRAVEL JOURNAL

Track all the places you’ve been and the trips you’ve been on. Nomadago will display a personal map of all the countries you’ve visited and give you a percentage of the world that you have seen.

FIND FRIENDS

Connect with other Nomadago users by posting your plans to the community, outside of your friend network. Or check out other users' public plans to see if you’ll be in the same area.

LOCATION SHARING

Share your current location and see where all your friends are currently using the world map 

COUNTRY SEARCH

Search for plans in a specific country to see all your friends who are currently in that country or will be on future dates.

CALENDAR CREATION

You are able to build out your travel calendar for as far in advance as you would like. This calendar can be seen by all of your friends so they know what you're up to. You can also check out their calendar.

PLAN EDITOR

Make plans to add to your calendar, set the location of where you are going, invite your friends to the plan, and discuss the trip in the comments.

PLAN FEED

Check out the feed to see all new plans being posted by your friends. Comment on any plans if you are interested in joining.


FUTURE LOCATIONS

Change the dates on the map to see where all of your friends plan to be on upcoming dates. This will give you ideas on your next location to go to and when to go.

CROSSING PATHS ALERTS

The app notifies you if you’re in the same city as a friend or if both you and a friend create a future plan to be in the same city at the same time.

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Passport 2024 is here! Update now and look back at your year of travel.

We have also made various improvements and fixes, with some fun little features that you can uncover as you explore the app.

Thanks everyone for your support in 2024. Keep exploring!

SEARCH AND BOOK ON THE MOVE
Choose from more than 90 flydubai destinations, pay online or choose to pay later, check in online, download your boarding pass and save it to your mobile wallet to save time at the airport. You can also book with any of our codeshare and interline partners. All that and more is at your fingertips.

apps.title: Singapore Airlines
apps.description:
Get ready for a greater experience from booking to boarding and beyond with the SingaporeAir app.

From user experience to personalised features, our app is designed to be fast, intuitive and a delight to use.

More features will be progressively added in future updates, but here are some key functions you can enjoy now:  

1. Explore, be inspired and get the latest deals on the go 
Where to next? Discover the latest fare deals to your favourite destinations. Planning your next destination has never been easier.      

2. Search, book and manage your flights
Search and book flights to your next getaway with Singapore Airlines or one of our many airline partners. You can now use your KrisFlyer miles, Apple Pay and Alipay to book your flights and preferred seats. Receive updates on your upcoming trips and pre-select your inflight meals and entertainment. After that, all you need to do is sit back and relax.

3. Skip the check-in queues 
To prepare for your trip, stay updated on the latest entry requirements with our travel advisory. Skip the queues at the airport, check in and download your boarding pass* on our app before departure. Select your seats and browse our digital menu to see what’s served onboard.

If you are departing from Singapore Changi Airport, generate your baggage tags on our app* during check-in and track the status of your baggage. Simply scan your mobile boarding pass at the check-in kiosks to print your baggage tags and proceed to the automated bag drop counters to deposit your checked bag. 

4. Manage your KrisFlyer account
Log in to your KrisFlyer account to keep track of your KrisFlyer miles balance and expiry, transaction statements and PPS value. PPS Club members can also connect with our customer support team via PPS Connect**. 

5. Experience the future of flying
Find out what’s playing on our award-winning KrisWorld inflight entertainment system. Curate playlists on your app and pick up right where you last left off between flights, or view your flight’s progress***.  

*Subject to regulatory requirements 
**This service is currently only available for registered PPS Club members with valid Singapore mobile numbers 
*** This feature is available on A350 and selected Boeing 777-300ER aircrafts 

Please also note that by downloading the SingaporeAir app, you agree to the terms and conditions, including the privacy policy, which can be found at http://www.singaporeair.com/en_UK/terms-conditions/ and http://www.singaporeair.com/en_UK/privacy-policy/

apps.title: Around Us: Travel guide & maps
apps.description:
Around Us is more than just an app—it’s an intuitive, and user-friendly travel companion designed for curious and savvy explorers. Whether you're dreaming of uncovering hidden gems close to home or exploring iconic destinations across the globe, Around Us is with you every step of the way, offering features to inspire and simplify your journeys.

Why choose Around Us?
A living, collaborative guide : Enhanced in real time by an active community of travelers, Around Us offers more than 12 million points of interest in 8 languages. Each location is carefully selected for its relevance and enriched with feedback from users like you.

An innovative interactive map : With dynamic bubbles, discover local trends at a glance. In Barcelona? Check out must-see sites like Park Güell, or uncover unique recommendations in quieter, more authentic streets. Thanks to our Tourist Score, explore smarter and avoid classic tourist traps. Navigate a larger, more immersive map that extends under the scroll bar and is compactly designed for smooth navigation. Swipe vertically to discover new places effortlessly.

Inspiring collaborative collections : Dive into collections created by other travelers, like a street art walk in Berlin or the best spots to photograph the northern lights in Iceland. Add your own hidden gems: a secret café, a breathtaking viewpoint, or a secluded beach. Note that the bookmark and collection features are now combined into a single, easily accessible icon on the map.

Stunning 3D immersion : Want a sneak peek of your next adventure? Explore interactive 3D views of the Egyptian pyramids, Norwegian fjords, and more. It’s like traveling from your couch!

Voice command : Simply ask, "Where are the best parks in New York?" or "Where can I swim on the French Riviera?" and let Around Us guide you.

Hyper-personalized filters : The search engine becomes the centerpiece of your navigation, divided into two sections: "Where?" to choose the location and "What?" to activate filters based on your preferences. Layer as many filters as you like, even using your bookmarks. A color-coded map helps you easily spot your favorite places. With more than 16,000 filters, find exactly what suits you—from hidden national parks with the “Nature Escape” filter to family-friendly activities with the “Family” filter.

A feature you’ll love! Plan your trip from A to Z:

Now you can view and estimate travel times to points of interest or between two points. Take advantage of handy shortcuts to launch searches quickly, even via Siri:
- Select your stops.
- Organize your itinerary.
- Visualize everything on a dynamic map with optimized routes (walking, cycling, or driving).
- Planning and enjoying your journey has never been easier!

Join an engaged community

Around Us doesn’t just guide you—it invites you to contribute. Create and share your itineraries, inspire other explorers, and help expand our database of addresses and tips. Around Us is a collaborative project, a borderless adventure, and an invitation to explore differently, emphasizing local expertise and authenticity.

Download the app today and be amazed by everything the world has to offer—right at your fingertips.

Around Us – Let curiosity lead your way.

apps.title: Travellink - Flights, Hotels
apps.description:
Thinking about travelling? Are you looking for a cheap flight? Download our app and make the trip of your dreams! We will also do the check-in for you, as soon as it is available, so you only have to worry about enjoying your trip.

We'll take care of everything: Finding cheap flights, showing you the best hotels and other accommodations for your stay, negotiating great deals on your rental car or arranging your ride from the airport to your destination. We've got you covered!

Cheap flights

Find cheap flights among our more than 600 airlines, for one way, return or multi-city!
Our wide variety of flights offers you from long distance flights to cheap low cost flights with airlines such as Ryanair, Easyjet, British Airways, Vueling, Iberia and more. Book your flights with us and you will be able to download your boarding passes directly from the app, in addition to tracking the status of any flight in real time. You will find the ideal flight and tickets at the cheapest price in our travel app.

Hotels

Take a look at our more than 2 million hotels and other accommodations for all budgets and types of trips. Search, book and compare hotel offers very easily.
You can book hotels like Melià Hotels and Resorts, Marriott, Eurostars, NH, Catalonia Hotels & Resorts and much more. Cancellation is free if you change your plans. We also offer discounts of up to 40% less in hotels if you book a flight with us.

Car rental

Do you want to complete your booking with a car rental? We offer cars from companies such as Hertz, Avis, Europcar, Alamo, Budget and up to 800 car rental agencies. Rent a car anytime, anywhere and travel at your own pace.

Sounds good, right? And that's not all!
Our travel app not only offers you cheap flights, hotel deals, and car rentals for your trips ... download the app and:

- Order your boarding passes for all your flights, and we will check-in as soon as it is available
- follow the status of any flight in real time with our new flight tracker feature
- Create an account and receive real time flight status notifications: gate numbers, baggage belts, delays or cancellations and more
- Check your flight itineraries, booking references or baggage allowances in the My Trips section, even without an internet connection!
- download our free travel guides and discover what to do at your destination, even if you don't have an internet connection

Travellink helps you to  find the best deals on flights, hotels and car rentals. Search, compare and book flight + hotel tickets in our travel app to enjoy a 40% discount.

We strive every day to make your travel dreams come true. If you had a positive experience with our app, would you mind rating us with 5 stars in the App Store? Thank you!

raw_data.releaseNotes: Nobody likes bugs. They scurry around hiding in the shadows and sneak up on us at the worst moments. Luckily, we’ve got a team devoted to squashing bugs. And that’s just what you can expect in this update. We squashed the bugs so the app will run more smoothly for you. Enjoy!

apps.title: Faye Travel Insurance
apps.description:
What if travel insurance did more than wait for something to go wrong - what if it helped things go right?

Faye does just that, delivering person-first, proactive, industry-leading coverage and care that protects your entire trip. Get covered in as little as 60 seconds with a custom, comprehensive plan that covers your trip, your stuff, your health, and even your pet.

Named one of the best travel insurance companies by The Wall Street Journal, the Faye travel insurance app goes the distance to redefine how you’re looked after when you’re on the road, providing:

The ability to insure your entire trip in as little as 60 seconds
Real-time trip monitoring and alerts (on things like flight changes and delays)
Emergency medical help with quick access to a nearby ER or pharmacy, as well as the ability to book an appointment with a network of 20K  telemedicine doctors in 21 languages


With Faye you can also:
Speak to customer experience specialists available 24/7 for proactive problem-solving and support when you need it most - anytime, anywhere, 365 days a year - even on weekends and holidays (yes, real humans!)
Easily file claims in minutes (just upload your documents to the app)
Receive quick reimbursements on approved claims and common travel snafus (even while you’re still in-trip) to your phone, done digitally thanks to Faye Wallet, a secure digital payments card given to every Faye user
Connect the moment you land abroad with eSIM – tap to activate travel data right from the app.
Store copies of your most precious travel docs securely with Safekeeping. Face ID protected, instantly accessible—even offline.
Use helpful widgets for local weather, currency conversions, local app recommendations and playlists to rock out to for every stage of your adventure



Built by avid travelers and insurance experts who believe that travel insurance can be more than a forgettable add-on but a must-have advantage, Faye helps keep you safe, informed and inspired to roam confidently.

We’re easy to get in touch with around the clock - chat with us in-app or email us at support@withfaye.com

What we cover

Pretty much everything and anything related to your travel well-being.

Your trip: If your trip gets delayed, interrupted or if you have to cancel, we'll be there to make it as stress-free as possible. You can even add on the ability to cancel for any reason.
 Your health: We cover emergency medical expenses you have during your trip, including ones related to COVID-19. Even if it means flying you home.
Your stuff: Phone or laptop gets stolen? Bags are delayed or damaged? We’ll help ya' out. Even with that favorite t-shirt of yours.

We also provide valuable add-ons that may be relevant to your trip: Pet care, Rental car care, Vacation rental damage protection, Extreme sports and Cancel for any reason protection.

Legal jargon

Terms of Service: https://www.withfaye.com/terms-of-use/
Privacy Policy: https://www.withfaye.com/privacy-policy/
Disclosures: https://www.withfaye.com/additional-disclosures/

Faye is the brand name for customizable travel protection plans offered by Zenner, Inc. and its subsidiaries including Zenner Insurance Services LLC, California license #6006067.

apps.title: Wander – Travel the World
apps.description:
Welcome to Wander!  We are a social network for the adventurous traveler to connect with other like-minded people during their travels.  Whether you are a traveler or a local adventurer, Wander is the gateway to meeting new friends and people that will broaden your perspective on life, culture, relationships and life-changing experiences.


Create that bucket list, share your adventures, plan your dream trips and see all the trending destinations.  Our platform makes it easy for you to connect with other travelers, locals at your destination, or simply meet other travelers coming to your hometown and other nearby people with the same passion.  Be that amazing host and show what your hometown has to offer.  Afterall, the best experiences are the ones created with new friends and possibly those travel love stories you often hear about.


Download now and discover the world.


Don't Go Alone!


Let us know how we're doing in the Reviews.

apps.title: SmartGuide travel guide & map
apps.description:
Smart Guide – Where All Journeys Begin
You Explore, We’ll Guide

SmartGuide is your personal tour guide to the world. Turn your phone into a personal audio tour guide to accompany you on your travel adventures.
Whether you are looking for a self-guided tour, audio traveler guide, city offline maps or you just want to know all the best sightseeing spots, fun activities, and authentic experiences for your travel destination, SmartGuide is the perfect choice for your travel guide needs.

ONE DIGITAL GUIDE APP FOR THE WHOLE WORLD
This personal guide app offers travel guides for over 1000 popular destinations around the world. Wherever your journey may take you, SmartGuide tours will meet you there!
You explore. We’ll guide.

SAFE CONTACT-LESS TOUR GUIDE
Crowded tour groups from all around the world are a prime breeding ground for respiratory viruses and similar bugs. This is not a souvenir you want to bring from your trip. Our virtual tour guide recommends different places to each tourist based on their individual interests and guides you safely outside of the crowds. Stay safe with a self-guided tour.

AUDIO GUIDE
The personal travel planner app is your audio guide to the world that lets you conveniently listen to a travel guide with interesting narratives from local guides that play automatically when you reach an interesting sight. Just let your phone talk to you and enjoy the scenery!

FREE SELF-GUIDED TOURS
SmartGuide won’t let you get lost and you won't miss any must-see sights. City-guide app uses GPS navigation to guide you around the city at your convenience at your own pace, for free. Gone are the days when you had to follow the crowd. Now you can use SmartGuide and travel whenever you want, however you want.
Sightseeing guide for the modern tripwolf on the hunt for undiscovered wonders of nature!

FIND HIDDEN GEMS AND ESCAPE TOURIST TRAPS
With extra local secrets, our guides provide you with inside information about the best spots off the beaten path. Escape the traps when you visit a city and immerse yourself in the culture trip. Get around like a local and discover the actual culture and heritage of any locality!

EVERYTHING IS OFFLINE.
Download your city guide and get the offline maps and guide with our premium option so you have the freedom to roam and discover the world like the tripwolf that you are, without worrying one bit about finding an internet connection. Your travel guide will be available offline in the form of verbal instructions from natives and if you are someone that prefers reading over listening, the transcripts of the audio guides are also available.

Get the most out of your world travel experience by exploring with SmartGuide: Your Personal Travel Audio Guide!

raw_data.releaseNotes:
Thanks for updating SmartGuide! What's new in this version:

Various improvements & fixes
- Not very noticeable but make the app more useful :)

Understand Your Cover

apps.title: Nomadtable: Solo Travel App
apps.description:
Traveling solo? Never eat, explore, or adventure alone again! Nomadtable connects solo travelers in real time, helping you meet like-minded people nearby, plan activities, and join future trips.

How It Works
- Join or create activities – Meet up for dinner, sightseeing, or casual hangouts.
- See who’s nearby – Find and connect with solo travelers in your current city.
- Future trip planning – Add your next destination and get matched in a group chat with travelers visiting at the same time.
- AI-powered recommendations – Get personalized activity and venue suggestions based on your location and interests.
- In-app messaging & group chats – Connect with travelers before and during your trip.

Premium Features (Nomadtable Plus) 
- See the full list of nearby travelers – Find everyone nearby, not just a limited selection.
- See who viewed your profile – See which nearby travelers check out your profile.
- Boost your profile – Appear near the top of the nearby travelers list.
- Unlimited AI activity suggestions – Unlock all AI-powered recommendations for meetups and activities.
- Full visibility of overlapping travelers – See the complete list of travelers visiting your future destinations.

Why Nomadtable?
- Real-time solo traveler meetups – Instantly connect with other travelers right now and join real-time activities happening near you.
- Safe & verified connections – Optional profile verification helps ensure genuine meetups with real travelers.
- Future trip planning made easy – Input your next destination and chat with others who overlap dates with you

Get Started in Seconds!
1. Sign up & set your profile (age, home country, languages spoken, travel interests).
2. See who's nearby or join a future trip group chat.
3. Start meeting fellow solo travelers today!

Download Nomadtable now & never explore alone again!

Terms of Use: https://terms.nomadtable.app
Privacy Policy: https://privacypolicy.nomadtable.app

- Join or create activities – Meet up for dinner, sightseeing, or casual hangouts.
- See who’s nearby – Find and connect with solo travelers in your current city.
- Future trip planning – Add your next destination and get matched in a group chat with travelers visiting at the same time.
- AI-powered recommendations – Get personalized activity and venue suggestions based on your location and interests.
- In-app messaging & group chats – Connect with travelers before and during your trip.

Premium Features (Nomadtable Plus) 
- See the full list of nearby travelers – Find everyone nearby, not just a limited selection.
- See who viewed your profile – See which nearby travelers check out your profile.
- Boost your profile – Appear near the top of the nearby travelers list.
- Unlimited AI activity suggestions – Unlock all AI-powered recommendations for meetups and activities.
- Full visibility of overlapping travelers – See the complete list of travelers visiting your future destinations.

Why Nomadtable?
- Real-time solo traveler meetups – Instantly connect with other travelers right now and join real-time activities happening near you.
- Safe & verified connections – Optional profile verification helps ensure genuine meetups with real travelers.
- Future trip planning made easy – Input your next destination and chat with others who overlap dates with you

Get Started in Seconds!

apps.title: Nomad: Travel Healthcare Jobs
apps.description:
Nomad: Travel Healthcare Jobs makes it easy to find and apply for traveling clinician jobs across a wide variety of healthcare disciplines, including travel nursing and allied health. Search for open positions in trusted facilities all over the country, chat with a team of experts as you navigate the hiring process, and track your shift hours easily.

GET WHERE YOU WANT TO GO FASTER
As soon as you complete your profile, you can apply for jobs in as little as one click. Explore job listings that fit your speciality, view a curated list of top matches, and subscribe to new job alerts. After you’ve submitted an application, you’ll get notifications about its status, as well as any incoming messages from a Nomad Navigator.

SEARCH TRANSPARENT JOB LISTINGS
You should feel confident and empowered to make informed decisions about your career. By using Nomad’s platform, you have access to full job descriptions, position requirements, facility information, and more. You can search jobs using a number of filters, including: specialty, location, start date, shift schedule, contract length, pay rate, and exclusivity.

REACH OUT FOR EXPERT SUPPORT
At any time during the application process, you can reach out via in-app messaging for support. A team of Nomad Navigators, our own healthcare industry experts, can help guide you through your placement by fielding questions, contacting your facility, and offering personalized solutions. Once you’re connected to a Navigator, you can chat with them from within the app, making it easy to communicate while on the go.

MANAGE YOUR HOURS
Not only can you search and apply for open travel healthcare positions from within the app, but you can also log your hours while on assignment and set up payment. If you accept an offer through Nomad, you’ll have access to a robust benefits package, including full healthcare coverage, 401(k) matching, malpractice insurance, and travel reimbursement, among other exciting features.

Download today and get started.
